videos.headline: Flea-flicker deep pass for a diving TD catch? It's as good as it sounds
videos.description: South Alabama is thinking of upsetting San Diego State for the second straight year when after the flea-flicker, Cole Garvin goes deep to Kevin Kutchera who lays out for the nasty touchdown catch putting the Jaguars up 14-6.
